<div id="Layer1" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2"> <p align="left"><font class="atitulohistoria"><b> Os doze de Inglaterra</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeautores"><b> Ant&oacute;nio Torrado</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>escreveu</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeilustrador"> <b>Cristina Malaquias</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>ilustrou</b></font></p></td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20">&nbsp;</td><td width="50%"> <img align="right" border="0" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer2" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">A hist&oacute;ria que vou contar ser&aacute; bom que, de aqui a alguns anos, a leiam em livro, para confirmarem se a contei como deve ser. Tenho as minhas d&uacute;vidas...</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer3" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Por enquanto talvez seja cedo, mas, em chegando o tempo certo, procurem-na n'<i> Os Lus&iacute;adas</i>, livro de muitas aventuras, que Lu&iacute;s de Cam&otilde;es escreveu em versos grandiosos e <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[506],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">resplandecentes</a>, onde sobressaem o orgulho de ser portugu&ecirc;s e a voz "nua e pura" de um grande poeta.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer4" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Desculpem-me este come&ccedil;o solene, t&atilde;o fora da minha maneira de contar, mas prometo que, de ora em diante, a hist&oacute;ria vai ganhar velocidade e galopar a toda a <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[507],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">brida</a>.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer5" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">A express&atilde;o "correr ou galopar a toda a <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[507],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">brida</a>", que &eacute; a r&eacute;dea do cavalo pegada ao freio, tem a ver com correrias &agrave; desfilada por estradas poeirentas, quando outro n&atilde;o era o meio de transporte de quem pretendia fazer longas viagens.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer6" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Nessas &eacute;pocas remotas, em que ainda n&atilde;o havia avi&otilde;es nem autom&oacute;veis nem comboios, os viajantes por terra tinham de saber andar a cavalo ou nunca iriam longe.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E, mesmo que fossem bons cavaleiros, muitos perigos defrontavam durante o caminho, al&eacute;m de que corriam o risco de se atrasarem e de n&atilde;o chegarem a tempo.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer7" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Veja-se o caso do Magri&ccedil;o, nome por que era conhecido &Aacute;lvaro Gon&ccedil;alves Coutinho, destemido cavaleiro da corte do nosso rei D. Jo&atilde;o I, n&atilde;o sei se est&atilde;o a par.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Como tudo isto se passou h&aacute; cerca de 600 anos, &eacute; natural que n&atilde;o se lembrem. Mas c&aacute; estou eu, &agrave; conta do Lu&iacute;s Vaz de Cam&otilde;es, para vos trazer alguns pormenores mais.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer8" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Deu-se o caso que doze damas da corte inglesa, de saias a arrastar e chap&eacute;us pontiagudos de fada, se sentiram ofendidas por uns <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[508],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">grosseir&otilde;es</a> duns nobres, de m&aacute; <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[509],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">catadura</a> e pior educa&ccedil;&atilde;o. Uns "holigans" do tempo, n&atilde;o sei se est&atilde;o a imaginar.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer9" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Como eles eram de for&ccedil;a e elas fracas, procuraram quem as substitu&iacute;sse e desse aos brutamontes a li&ccedil;&atilde;o merecida. O pior &eacute; que a m&aacute; reputa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos alarves cavaleiros assustava e n&atilde;o houve um &uacute;nico ingl&ecirc;s (e j&aacute; eram bastantes milh&otilde;es!) capaz de defender as damas.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer10" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Inconsol&aacute;veis, as meninas de chap&eacute;us de fada foram chorar-se ao velho Duque de Lencastre, que tamb&eacute;m j&aacute; n&atilde;o estava em idade de valer-lhes. Mas o Duque recordava-se da coragem dos portugueses por, noutros tempos, ao lado deles ter batalhado.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer11" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Vai da&iacute; recomendou-lhes:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Quem pode salvar a vossa honra ofendida e fazer frente aos <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[510],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">marmanjos</a> ingleses s&atilde;o aqueles bravos rapazes l&aacute; de baixo. Escrevam-lhes a pedir socorro.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Foi o que elas fizeram, na mais elegante das caligrafias e com as mais sedutoras e doces palavras.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer12" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Candidatos portugueses n&atilde;o faltaram, mas s&oacute; podiam ir doze a Inglaterra, sen&atilde;o despovoava-se o reino.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Embarcaram os jovens portugueses na foz do Douro com seus <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[511],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">aprestos</a> e cavalos. Todos menos um, o tal Magri&ccedil;o, que preferiu viajar, montado no seu cavalo e j&aacute; de lan&ccedil;a e armadura, como se Inglaterra fosse ali adiante.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer13" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Olha que n&atilde;o chegas a tempo - lembraram-lhe os companheiros. - V&ecirc; no que te metes!
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Mas o Magri&ccedil;o fez de conta que enjoava a viagem por mar e enfiou pela terra adiante. Um <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[512],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">estir&atilde;o</a>.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer14','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer14" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Os onze cavaleiros portugueses atravessaram de barco o Mar do Norte e desembarcaram em Inglaterra, onde foram muito amimados pelas damas ofendidas. S&oacute; uma estava triste, a que, em sorte, iria ser defendida pelo pouco pontual Magri&ccedil;o.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer14','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer15','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer14','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer15" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Contra os doze ingleses se apresentaram os onze portugueses. Aquilo n&atilde;o era um desafio de futebol, mas torneio em campo aberto, com elmos, <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[513],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">grevas</a> e <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[514],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">arneses</a> e lan&ccedil;as e espad&otilde;es. Um caso s&eacute;rio.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Na tribuna das damas, a menina Magri&ccedil;a (chamemos-lhe assim, por comodidade...) chorava a sua solid&atilde;o.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer15','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer14','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer16','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer15','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer16" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Mastigam os cavalos os freios, escumando e raspando o ch&atilde;o, empunham os soldados as trombetas, para dar come&ccedil;o &agrave; li&ccedil;a, refulgem ao Sol as lan&ccedil;as de a&ccedil;o e as armaduras de ferro e, onze contra doze, vai come&ccedil;ar a luta de vida ou de morte.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Repentinamente, levanta-se nas tribunas o povo, em grande alvoro&ccedil;o.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer16','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer15','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer17','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer16','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer17" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Todos viram o rosto, &agrave; procura da causa do reboli&ccedil;o. &Eacute; Magri&ccedil;o, pronto para o combate, que chega, envolto numa nuvem de p&oacute;.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">A Magri&ccedil;a inglesa sustem as l&aacute;grimas e sorri como um arco-&iacute;ris, depois da tempestade.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Ao som das tubas, largam r&eacute;deas, esporeiam os cavalos, baixam lan&ccedil;as e "fere a terra fogo".</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer17','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer16','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer18','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer17','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer18" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Dos cavalos o <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[515],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">estr&eacute;pito</a> parece
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Que faz que o ch&atilde;o debaixo todo treme;
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O cora&ccedil;&atilde;o no peito que estremece,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">De quem os olha, se alvoro&ccedil;a e teme.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer18','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer17','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer19','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer18','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer19" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Qual do cavalo voa, que n&atilde;o dece;
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Qual, com cavalo em terra dando, geme;
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Qual vermelhas as armas faz de brancas;
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Qual com os penachos do elmo a&ccedil;oute as ancas.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer19','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer18','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer20','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer19','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer20" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E os doze valentes portugueses derribaram os doze brutos ingleses. Para os nossos a palma da vit&oacute;ria e as damas vencedoras e com gl&oacute;ria.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Depois, j&aacute; se v&ecirc;, houve festa da rija, nos pa&ccedil;os do Duque de Lencastre.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer20','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer19','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer21','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer20','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer21" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Recolhe o Duque os doze vencedores
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Nos seus pa&ccedil;os, com festa e alegria;
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Cozinheiros ocupa e ca&ccedil;adores,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Das damas a formosa companhia,</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer21','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer20','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer22','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer21','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer22" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Que querem dar aos seus libertadores
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Banquetes mil, cada hora e cada dia,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Enquanto se det&ecirc;m em Inglaterra,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">At&eacute; tornar &agrave; doce e querida terra.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer22','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer21','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer23','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer22','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer23" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Parece que o Magri&ccedil;o se demorou mais uns tempos e n&atilde;o regressou com os companheiros. J&aacute; era mania...
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%"></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer23','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer22','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="35%"><a href="imprimir.pdf" target="_blank"> <img src="../../../images/impre.jpg" align="left" border="0" width="20" height="20"></a><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow('../../../pop_votar.aspx?Mes=06&Dia=10','','menubar=no,width=270,height=170')"><img src="../../../images/votar_over.gif" align="right" border="0" width="67" height="20"></a></td></tr></table></div> 
